  "DesertTrader2.RacerGuy": "Step right up and witness wonders!",
  "DesertTrader1.RacerGuy": "Welcome, traveler! Ready to make a trade?",
  
// Lines for Pierre at various festivals
  "PierreJellyfish": "Rare items that shine just like a Moonlight Jelly! Don't miss out!",
  "PierreEgg": "Exclusive items on sale! Get them before the day ends, or you'll miss out!",
  "PierreFeast": "Festive goodies to warm your holiday! Grab yours while they last!",
  "PierreFlower": "Beautiful flowers to charm your dance partner! Pick them up before the last dance!",
  "PierreLuau": "Exotic decorations to make {{FarmName}} Farm the talk of the town! Grab them while you can!",
  "PierreSpirit": "Spooky decorations for building the scariest barn! Get them before they vanish!",

// Line for the clinic, made generic because it could be spoken by either Harvey or Maru.
  "MaruClinic": "A quick sip of one of these, and you'll be back to full speed in no time.",
  "HarveyClinic": "Ah, welcome! Good to see you're minding your health.",
  
// Alex  
  "AlexIceCream": "How about some cool ice cream to beat the heat?",

//1.9.0 Rotation Concession lines
  "Concessions1.Daena": "Sweets? Drinks? I've got you!",
  "Concessions2.Daena": "You're going to regret not getting a treat halfway through the film. Just saying.",
  "Concessions3.Daena": "Your guest looks hungry. Come on, be nice. Get them something good!",
  "Concession.Daena": "Welcome to the snack stand! Fancy grabbing something tasty for your guest?",
  "ConcessionAlone.Daena": "On your own, are you? If you bring a guest, you can order them a treat! Makes film night way better, trust me.",
  "ConcessionPurchased.Daena": "So you want the {0}, right? We'll drop it off at {1}'s seat once the film starts!",
  "ConcessionAfterMovie.Daena": "Film's over! Was it good? If not, at least the treats were!",
  "Concessions1.Naufal": "Oh, we've got some drinks too if you're feeling thirsty!",
  "Concessions2.Naufal": "A good treat makes the film even better!",
  "Concessions3.Naufal": "Your guest looks like they might be a bit peckish... maybe a little something for them?",  
  "Concession.Naufal": "Oh, um... welcome! Would you like a treat for your guest?",
  "ConcessionAlone.Naufal": "Oh! Just so you know, if you come with a guest, you can order them a treat. It's a nice way to make the film even more special!",
  "ConcessionPurchased.Naufal": "You ordered the {0}, right? We'll make sure {1} gets it once the film starts!",
  "ConcessionAfterMovie.Naufal": "How was the film? Um, I hope you had a nice time!",
  
// 1.9.0 Rotation Movie Ticket Lines
  "BoxOffice.Default": "Got a mate you fancy inviting? Just pass them a ticket and there you go: film night!",
  "BoxOffice.Naufal": "If you'd like, you can give one to a mate and invite them to join you!",  

//1.9.0 Central Station cameo
  "CentralStation.Merchant": "Merchant",  
  "CentralStation.SailorCat": "Sailor Cat",    
  "CentralStation.Naufal.1": "Oh, um... hi. Sorry, I thought you were my shift manager for a second.",
  "CentralStation.Naufal.2": "I do a lot of part-time jobs... It's nice to help out, but I, uh, sometimes forget which one I'm off to.",
  "CentralStation.Naufal.3": "People always tell me I should have a break, but... I like keeping busy. It makes me feel useful.",
  "CentralStation.Daena.1": "Ever worked customer service in a place like this? Feels like a battle royale.",
  "CentralStation.Daena.2": "Part-time work? More like part-time survival. One minute you're flipping burgers, the next you're wrangling tourists.",
  "CentralStation.Daena.3": "My schedule's a mess, but hey, I get to see all sorts of weird stuff.",
  "CentralStation.Daena.4": "Like that flamingo. Why is there a flamingo??",	
  "CentralStation.Mark.1": "Another job, another shift... I just want to be in bed, mate.",
  "CentralStation.Mark.2": "You ever have a day where you wake up tired, work tired, then come home even more tired? Yeah. That's every day.",
  "CentralStation.Merchant.1": "No wares today, traveller. Perhaps only a moment of rest before the next journey.",
  "CentralStation.Merchant.2": "Strange, isn't it? A place so full of people, yet no one stays for long. We are all just passing through.",  
  "CentralStation.SailorCat.1": "Spent nine lives at sea and still get seasick on a train. Ain't that somethin'?",
  "CentralStation.SailorCat.2": "I'm used to nap in coils of rope. Train benches don't curl right.",   

